  "description": "## Deep Component Audit — hx-breadcrumb\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-breadcrumb/`\n**Sub-components:** hx-breadcrumb-item\n**wc-mcp Health Score:** breadcrumb=92 (A), breadcrumb-item=100 (A)\n**Known issues:** Property '_itemCount' missing description.\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** — `--hx-` tokens. Separator styling via tokens. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** — WCAG 2.1 AA. nav[aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\"]. Structured list. Current page indicator (aria-current).\n3. **Functionality** — Dynamic item count. Separator customization. Overflow/truncation. Link vs text items. Slot behavior.\n4. **TypeScript** — Strict. No `any`. _itemCount should be properly typed.\n5. **CSS/Styling** — Shadow DOM. CSS Parts for separators. Responsive truncation.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** — Fix _itemCount description. Verify both components.\n7. **Tests** — 80%+ coverage. Dynamic items. Navigation. ARIA structure.\n8. **Storybook** — Multiple items. Overflow. Custom separators.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** — Twig menu integration. Drupal breadcrumb block.\n10. **Portability** — CDN-ready.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
